OL,3,CPolice to review death of man
OL,4,Cfollowing Cumberland Infirmary
OL,5,Callegations
OL,7,FPolice in Cumbria are reviewing the
OL,8,Fdeath of a man who died weeks after
OL,9,Fundergoing a leg amputation at the
OL,10,FCumberland Infirmary.
OL,12,FIt comes after ITV News Border
OL,13,Fexclusively revealed a number of
OL,14,Fallegations being levelled at the
OL,15,Fhospital by the family of Bill
OL,16,FTrotter, who died last year. The
OL,17,Ffamily have yet to bury Mr Trotter,
OL,18,Fbelieving his body could be needed as
OL,19,Fthey investigate the treatment he
OL,20,Freceived prior to his death.
