OL,5,Callegations
OL,7,FHowever Cumbria's Coroner has rejected
OL,8,Ftheir calls for an inquest, satisfied
OL,9,Fthat Mr Trotter died from natural
OL,10,Fcauses. She told ITV News she couldn't
OL,11,Fcomment on individual cases.
