OL,3,CPolice to review death of man
OL,4,Cfollowing Cumberland Infirmary
OL,5,Callegations
OL,7,FThe 73-year-old was admitted to
OL,8,FCumberland Infirmary in Carlisle in
OL,9,FMay last year, after a course of
OL,10,Fantibiotics to clear an infection in
OL,11,Fhis toes failed and he became
OL,12,Fincreasingly unwell. What followed,
OL,13,Fhis children told ITV News in an
OL,14,Finterview, was a catalogue of errors
OL,15,Fin care over the following weeks
OL,16,Fbefore his death.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/8
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
