OL,3,CPolice to review death of man
OL,4,Cfollowing Cumberland Infirmary
OL,5,Callegations
OL,7,FIn particular, Michael Trotter and his
OL,8,Fsister Kelly believe hospital staff
OL,9,Ffailed to fit a catheter following
OL,10,Ftheir Father's operation, potentially
OL,11,Fleading to him developing retention
OL,12,Frelated urinary sepsis. They further
OL,13,Fclaim that Mr Trotter was misdiagnosed
OL,14,F- his original diagnosis of gangrene
OL,15,Fhaving later been changed to a rare
OL,16,Fcondition called calciphylaxis
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/8
