OL,3,CPolice to review death of man
OL,4,Cfollowing Cumberland Infirmary
OL,5,Callegations
OL,7,FMoreover, the pair allege that their
OL,8,FFather was given a large dose of long-
OL,9,Flasting insulin before he died,
OL,10,Fwithout the knowledge of the
OL,11,Fhospital's diabetes team. They believe
OL,12,Fthis caused him to slip into a
OL,13,Fdiabetic coma from which he never
OL,14,Fawoke.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/8
