OL,3,CPolice to review death of man
OL,4,Cfollowing Cumberland Infirmary
OL,5,Callegations
OL,7,FIn a statement Cumbria Police said:
OL,8,F"The death of Mr Trotter was
OL,9,Finvestigated, which included
OL,10,Fassessment of the findings from a full
OL,11,FPost Mortem examination, and the
OL,12,Ffamily were subsequently informed that
OL,13,Fno criminal proceedings would be taken.
OL,15,F"After additional information has
OL,16,Frecently been provided, Cumbria Police
OL,17,Fis currently carrying out a further
OL,18,Freview.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/8
