OL,3,CPolice to review death of man
OL,4,Cfollowing Cumberland Infirmary
OL,5,Callegations
OL,7,F"This review is ongoing and it would
OL,8,Fnot be appropriate to comment further
OL,9,Fat this stage."
OL,11,FThe siblings are also considering
OL,12,Ftaking civil action against North
OL,13,FCumbria Integrated Care Trust, which
OL,14,Fruns Cumberland Infirmary, over the
OL,15,Falleged failings.
OL,17,FIn a statement, the trust said: "We
OL,18,Fwould like to extend our deepest
OL,19,Fsympathies to the family of Mr Trotter
OL,20,Fat what is a very upsetting and
OL,21,Ftraumatic time.
